LOOK: Look at your surroundings or an object

Syntax: look
        look <object>
        look at <object>
        look in <container>

DESCRIPTION:
  Without arguments, redisplays your current room description, exits,
  NPCs, and objects present.

  With an argument, examines the specified object, NPC, or player.

EXAMPLES:
  look
  look at the falconer
  look in backpack

SEE ALSO: examine, brief
